  <data name="Submission.LegalDisclaimer" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>KROIRA is a media player and source manager. KROIRA does not provide channels, streams, playlists, subscriptions, or media content. Users are responsible for adding only authorized sources and for complying with applicable provider terms and laws. KROIRA does not bypass DRM, paywalls, authentication, or access controls.</value>
