  <data name="Submission.LongDescription" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>KROIRA IPTV is a Windows media player and source manager for user-provided M3U playlists, Xtream providers, and Stalker portals. It helps organize live channels, VOD libraries, guide data, favorites, continue-watching state, and source diagnostics on this device. KROIRA does not provide channels, streams, playlists, subscriptions, accounts, credentials, or media content.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Submission_LongDescription" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>KROIRA IPTV is a Windows media player and source manager for user-provided M3U playlists, Xtream providers, and Stalker portals. It helps organize live channels, VOD libraries, guide data, favorites, continue-watching state, and source diagnostics on this device. KROIRA does not provide channels, streams, playlists, subscriptions, accounts, credentials, or media content.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Submission.MetadataProviderSummary" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>When metadata enrichment is used, KROIRA may contact metadata or artwork providers such as TMDb, plus image URLs supplied by user-configured sources. KROIRA does not send source passwords or provider tokens to TMDb.</value>
  </data>
