  <data name="Submission.RunFullTrustJustification" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>KROIRA is a packaged WinUI 3 desktop application that uses the Windows App SDK full-trust desktop entry point and local native playback components. The runFullTrust capability is required for the packaged desktop app launch model and native media playback integration; it is not used to bypass DRM, paywalls, authentication, or access controls.</value>
